summary:
I am an energetic and ambitious individual who has developed a mature and responsible approach to any task that I undertake or situation I am presented with. 

My communication skills and passion for connecting with people have been my main drives in my career.
My academic background and work experiences in Europe, North America and Central America helped me realize my passion for working with people and strengthened my skills in Event Management, negotiation, creativity, organization, communication, and time management.

As a "people-person" I am all about my clients' satisfaction and I use this as my fuel through the most demanding projects.
